description: Just looking for a few open-minded birds to hang out, play dead and snuggle.
I'm hypoallergenic and love to lounge in the sun. You'll often find me napping in your windowsill or on the patio.
I'm a super intelligent social gal who loves to play at the dog park with new friends. Very obedient and well-behaved.
Gentle, loving pup who is great with children and loves to be held. Favorite games include indoor fetch and ball chasing.
Loves to take walks in the park and try new treats. I know how to pile my toys up in one spot when I'm done playing!

I'm hypoallergenic and love to lounge in the sun. You'll often find me napping in your windowsill or on the patio.
Slow and steady, I'm the perfect companion. I'll snuggle next to you for hours and mind very well when asked to do something.
I'll entertain myself for hours chasing my tail or rolling around on the floor. I love playing outside when I can.
The best traveling pup you'll ever meet. I love making new friends everywhere.
